									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="Following a recent escalation in insurgent activity, Coalition assets have confirmed that Farabad has become a major logistics hub for enemy operations throughout Takistan. <br/><br/>    " \n "Arms trafficking, recruitment, and coordinated attacks have spiked, destabilizing nearby regions. The town's proximity to key mountain passes makes it a strategic node for insurgent movement. <br/><br/>    " \n "Jalali Khara, a known insurgent commander and orchestrator of several ambushes on NATO convoys, has been positively ID'd operating in the sector. Additionally, weapons caches used to arm local cells have been located and must be neutralized. " \n "";
